Quote:  The terms "Bodgie" and "Widgie" are peculiar to the middle 20th Century, but the characteristics are not... In the under-privileged masses the counterparts of Bodgies were variously styled as 'yahoos', 'larrikins', 'hooligans' and 'yobs'. The 'playboy' of upper class society is the "Bodgie" of the poor.
